'''Di konosementu''' tin un proseso sistemátika di mes ku controle bai organisá e konosementu di e forma un komprobante splicacion i produccion di [[Universo|mundu]].

Di konosementu contemporary e enkuanto supdividí den ciencia natural, ku e fin di studia e mundu material. e ciencia social, ku ta studia na humano i ku e sosiedat, i e siensia formal, e estudio di e lógiko i e matemátika. E siensia formeel ta bai fini ekskluí, komo ku no ta dependé empíriko servisionan.<ref>{{Cite web|author=Editorial Staff|date=March 7, 2008|url=http://www.cnrt.scsu.edu/~psc152/A/branches.htm|title=The Branches of Science|publisher=South Carolina State University|accessdate=October 28, 2014}}</ref> e Disiplina na utilidat di konosementu, manera e ingeniero i di salú, por ta konsiderá e manera siensia aplica.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.seedmagazine.com/news/2007/03/scientific_method_relationship.php|title=Scientific Method: Relationships among Scientific Paradigms|last=|first=|date=March 7, 2008|website=|publisher=Seed Magazine|author=Editorial Staff|accessdate=September 12, 2007}}</ref>

For di clásica na kla for di siglo 19, e konosementu manera un tipo di konosementu tabata mas estriktamente mará na e [[filosofia]] di e ta awor i den e mundu di Pabou, e fin "filosofia natural", un biaha e barco di kunuku di estudio den e actividad ta sosiedat ku e konosementu, manera e astronomy, e salú i e físiko.[./Science#cite_note-FOOTNOTELindberg20073-7 <span class="mw-reflink-text"><nowiki>[5]</nowiki></span>]{{sfn|Lindberg|2007|p=3}}[./Science#cite_note-8 <span class="mw-reflink-text"><nowiki>[laar a apa 3]</nowiki></span>]{{efn|Isaac Newton's [[Philosophiae Naturalis Principia Mathematica]] (1687), for example, is translated "Mathematical Principles of Natural Philosophy", and reflects the then-current use of the words "[[natural philosophy]]", akin to "systematic study of nature"}} Sinembargo, durante e Edat di Oro Islamita base di e metodo sientífiko a wòrdu nombrá dor di Ibn den en Haha den su ''Buki Tica''.<ref name="Haq">[//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Syed_Nomanul_Haq Haq, Syed] (2009). </ref><ref>[//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/G._J._Toomer G. J. Toomer]. </ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.light2015.org/Home/ScienceStories/1000-Years-of-Arabic-Optics.html|title=International Year of Light - Ibn Al-Haytham and the Legacy of Arabic Optics|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Al-Khalili, Jim|author=Al-Khalili, Jim|date=4 January 2009|work=BBC News|title=The 'first true scientist'|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/7810846.stm|accessdate=24 September 2013}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last=Gorini|first=Rosanna|title=Al-Haytham the man of experience. First steps in the science of vision|url=http://www.ishim.net/ishimj/4/10.pdf|journal=Journal of the International Society for the History of Islamic Medicine|volume=2|issue=4|pages=53–55|date=October 2003|format=PDF|accessdate=2008-09-25|ref=harv}}</ref> Miéntras ku bon planificacion di mundu material na e antiguo India i Griego den e aire, e tera, e kandela i awa tabata filosofo media, e Medio Easterns utilidat realisá i e conservacion experimenta pa klasifiká e material.<ref name="Jim">''[//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Science_and_Islam_(documentary) Science and Islam]'', [//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jim_Al-Khalili Jim Al-Khalili]. </ref>

